  "title": "Valentine's Day Delivery Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are a florist seeking a delivery driver with their own car or van to deliver fresh flowers on 14 Feb from 8am to 10pm. This is a part-time, contract, temporary, or freelance role with attractive pay and meals provided.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive your own car or van to deliver fresh flowers accurately and on time to customers</li><li>Plan and follow delivery routes to ensure efficient and timely deliveries on 14 Feb</li><li>Handle flowers carefully to maintain quality during transport and delivery</li><li>Communicate clearly with the florist team about delivery status and any issues</li><li>Maintain a clean and safe vehicle to support safe delivery operations</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Job Types: Part-time, Contract, Temporary, Freelance</li><li>Work Location: In person</li><li>Work Date and Hours: 14 Feb, 8am to 10pm</li><li>Meals provided</li><li>Very attractive pay</li></ul>",
